OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FElectric car drivers must  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay tax from 2025          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Electric cars will no longer be exempt 
OL,6, from vehicle excise duty from April    
OL,7, 2025, the chancellor has said.         
OL,9,FAnnouncing the change as part of his   
OL,10,FAutumn Statement, Jeremy Hunt said the 
OL,11,Fmove was designed to make the motoring 
OL,12,Ftax system "fairer".                   
OL,14,FThe RAC motoring group said it did not 
OL,15,Fexpect the change to dampen demand for 
OL,16,Felectric vehicles (EVs).               
OL,18,FBut others, including the AA, warned   
OL,19,Fthe move would reduce the incentive to 
OL,20,Fswitch to EVs.                         
